Design document created at `docs/design/automation-article-saving.md` (22,977 bytes).

**Key design decisions:**
- **Automatic full-page content extraction** via new `GET_FULL_PAGE_CONTENT` message handler with heuristic DOM stripping (no external readability dependency)
- **AI-powered metadata enrichment** service (`packages/ai/src/services/enrichArticle.ts`) with local heuristic fallback for topic/difficulty/tags/summary prediction
- **Three one-click save paths**: toolbar icon click, context menu ("Save Page as IELTS Reading"), keyboard shortcut (`Ctrl+Shift+A`)
- **Schema extension**: adds `contentHtml`, `wordCount`, `readingTimeMinutes`, `author`, `publishDate`, `contentHash`, `summary`, `source` to `ExtensionArticleEntry`
- **Smart de-duplication** by URL and content hash
- **Batch article capture mode** for session-based accumulation
